---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="launch">
  <div class="launch__stars" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="launch__content">
    <h1 class="launch__title">Fatal Conversion</h1>
    <p class="launch__subtitle">The Ariane 5 Flight V88 Catastrophe</p>
    <p class="launch__tagline">Thirty-six seconds. One integer. Half a billion dollars.</p>

    <a href="#mission-briefing" class="launch__cta">
      Land Safely
      <Icon name="ic:round-keyboard-arrow-down" />
    </a>

    <p class="launch__intro">
      On June 4, 1996, the maiden flight of Ariane 5 ended 36.7 seconds after
      liftoff. The cause was not a faulty sensor, not a structural failure,
      not weather. It was an integer that no longer fit.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .launch {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .launch__stars {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 20px 30px, white, transparent),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 120px 80px, white, transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 200px 150px, white, transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 300px 40px, white, transparent),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 400px 200px, white, transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 500px 100px, white, transparent);
    background-repeat: repeat;
    background-size: 550px 300px;
    opacity: 0.6;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .launch__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 42rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .launch__title {
    font-family: 'Lora Variable', serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .launch__subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .launch__tagline {
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .launch__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    background: #2fae4e;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(47, 174, 78, 0.4);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .launch__cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(47, 174, 78, 0.5);
  }

  .launch__cta:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid white;
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .launch__cta :global(svg) {
    animation: bounce 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(3px); }
  }

  .launch__intro {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .launch__cta :global(svg) {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>